## **Key Feature Importance**

The following features were identified as the most important for the model's performance, based on Random Forest and XGBoost feature importance scores:

| Feature Name | Description |
| ----- | ----- |
| EXT\_SOURCE\_2 | External credit score, highly correlated with target outcome |
| EXT\_SOURCE\_3 | Another external credit score |
| AMT\_CREDIT\_x | Total credit amount requested |
| DAYS\_EMPLOYED | Number of days employed |
| AMT\_INCOME\_TOTAL | Total income of the individual |
| AMT\_CREDIT\_y | Alternative credit amount |
| OCCUPATION\_TYPE | Type of occupation |
| DAYS\_LAST\_DUE | Days till the last payment due |
| CNT\_FAM\_MEMBERS | Number of family members |
| AMT\_REQ\_CREDIT\_BUREAU\_MON | Number of credit bureau inquiries in the past month |
| FLAG\_OWN\_REALTY | Whether the individual owns real estate |
| AGE\_GROUP | Age category derived from birth data |
| NAME\_INCOME\_TYPE | Type of income (e.g., salary, business) |
| NAME\_CASH\_LOAN\_PURPOSE | Purpose of the cash loan |
| FLAG\_OWN\_CAR | Whether the individual owns a car  |
